com.commander4j.db

Class JDBMaterialCustomerData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.commander4j.db.JDBMaterialCustomerData

  • public class JDBMaterialCustomerData
extends java.lang.Object
    JDBMaterialCustomerData class is used to insert/update/delete the APP_MATERIAL_CUSTOMER_DATA table. This table is keyed on MATERIAL, CUSTOMER_ID and DATA_ID.
